quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  30,11,UAllâh Uyiqala ekuqaleni indalo; Uya kuphinda ayiphinde; nize nina nibuyiselwe kuYe
  30,12,Ke kaloku Mhla iYure yafika izaphula-mthetho ziya kuphelelwa lithemba
  30,13,"Kananjalo kubo akuyi kubakho namnye umthetheleli kumahlulelane abo, yaye baya (kuqala) bangakholwa3 kumahlulelane abo"
  30,14,Kananjalo ngeMini yokufika kweYure ngaloo Mini baya kwahlukaniswa
  30,15,"Abo bakholwayo, benza izenzo zobulungisa, baya kuba seMyezweni (ePaladesi) bevuya"
  30,16,"Ke bona abo baye bangakholwa baphika iiVesi zeThu nendibano yakuBomi oBuzayo, abo baya kuziswa esohlwayweni"
  30,17,"Ngoko ke mzukiseni uAllâh xa nifikelela kungcwalazo, naxa nifikelela kwintseni"
  30,18,Yaye iindumiso (zonke) zezaKhe emazulwini nasemhlabeni. Kananjalo Mzukiseni Yena emalanga nasemvakwemini
  30,19,"Yena Ukhupha abaphilileyo kwabafileyo, Akhuphe abafileyo kwabaphilileyo, Abuyisele ubomi emhlabeni emveni kokuba ubungasenabomi. Nani niya kubuyiselwa (ebomini) ngolo hlobo"